```
(Backfill function is idempotent — safe to call on every startup.)

### Step 5: Frontend Status Config

**`src/features/sidebar/lib/status.ts`** — Add workflow status config (import WorkspaceStatus):
```typescript
export const WORKFLOW_STATUS_CONFIG: Record<WorkspaceStatus, {
  label: string;
  color: string;
}> = {
  "backlog":     { label: "Backlog",     color: "text-muted-foreground" },
  "in-progress": { label: "In Progress", color: "text-amber-500" },
  "in-review":   { label: "In Review",   color: "text-purple-500" },
